  dialogue:
  - Hmmm. How did I end up here? Oh well.
  - Hmmm. That thing looks tasty! That pink swirly thing!
  - Hmmm. Did I order already? I want that pink swirly thing!
  responses:
  - responseText: What happened to your lower half?
